<div style="padding:30px 20px; color:#333;">
    <h2>Hello,</h2>
    <p>
        <strong>UPCOMING DEADLINE:</strong> The screening date for the following property will expire in 3 days:
    </p>
    <table style="margin:20px 0; border-collapse:collapse; border:1px solid #ddd;">
        <tr style="background-color:#f8f9fa;">
            <td style="padding:8px 12px; border:1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Property Control Number:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding:8px 12px; border:1px solid #ddd;"><%= property.property_control_number %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding:8px 12px; border:1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Property Name:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding:8px 12px; border:1px solid #ddd;"><%= property.property_name %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background-color:#f8f9fa;">
            <td style="padding:8px 12px; border:1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Surplus Release Date:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding:8px 12px; border:1px solid #ddd;"><%= new Date(property.property_surplus_release_date).toLocaleDateString() %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding:8px 12px; border:1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Property Status:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding:8px 12px; border:1px solid #ddd;"><%= property.property_status %></td>
        </tr>
        <% if (property.request && property.request.doneeAccount) { %>
        <tr style="background-color:#f8f9fa;">
            <td style="padding:8px 12px; border:1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Organization:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding:8px 12px; border:1px solid #ddd;"><%= property.request.doneeAccount.organization?.name %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding:8px 12px; border:1px solid #ddd;"><strong>State:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding:8px 12px; border:1px solid #ddd;"><%= property.request.doneeAccount.state?.stateName %></td>
        </tr>
        <% } %>
    </table>
    
    <div style="background-color:#d4edda; border:1px solid #c3e6cb; border-radius:4px; padding:15px; margin:20px 0;">
        <p style="margin:0; color:#155724;"><strong>Upcoming Action Required:</strong> Please review this property within the next 3 days as the screening date will expire on <%= new Date(property.property_surplus_release_date).toLocaleDateString() %>.</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>Please log into American Surplus to review the property details and plan your action accordingly.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please contact the American Surplus support team.</p>
    <p>Thanks,<br>American Surplus Team</p>
</div>
